<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Barlow:wght@400;700&family=Roboto:wght@400;500;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style type="text/css">
      span {
        font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif !important;
        font-weight: 400;
        color: #222;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div
      style="
        display: grid;
        width: 760px;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        border: 1px solid #f2f2f2;
      "
    >
      <div
        style="
          display: grid;
          padding: 0px 40px;
          grid-template-columns: auto auto;
        "
      >
        <img
          style="
            grid-column-start: 1;
            grid-column-end: 3;
            margin-top: 50px;
            width: 70px;
            object-fit: contain;
          "
          alt="logo"
          src="http://13.125.60.249:5000/download?id=510"
        />
        <span
          style="
            grid-column-start: 1;
            grid-column-end: 3;
            color: #222;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif !important;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 36px;
          "
          ><%= title %></span
        >
        <span
          style="
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 22px;
            color: #777;
            margin-top: 12px;
            grid-column-start: 1;
            grid-column-end: 3;
          "
          ><%= message %>
        </span>
        <span
          style="
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif !important;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 16px;
            grid-column-start: 1;
            grid-column-end: 3;
            margin-top: 60px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid#ed7730;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 3px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-top-left-radius: 3px;
            line-height: 19px;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
          "
          ><%= subTitle %></span
        >

        <span
          style="
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 19px;
            grid-column-start: 1;
            grid-column-end: 3;
            color: #222;
            margin-bottom: 13px;
          "
        >
          <%= codeTitle %> :
          <span
            stlye=" font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif !important;font-weight: 700;"
          >
            <%= code %></span
          >
        </span>

        <span
          style="
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 19px;
            grid-column-start: 1;
            grid-column-end: 3;
            color: #222;
            margin-bottom: 13px;
          "
        >
          <%= codeTitle1 %> :
          <span
            stlye=" font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif !important;font-weight: 700;"
          >
            <%= code1 %></span
          >
        </span>

        <span
          style="
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 19px;
            grid-column-start: 1;
            grid-column-end: 3;
            color: #222;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
          "
        >
          <%= codeTitle2 %> :
          <span
            stlye=" font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif !important;font-weight: 700;"
          >
            <%= code2 %></span
          >
        </span>
      </div>
      <div
        style="
          display: grid;
          grid-template-columns: auto auto;
          background-color: #f2f2f2;
          padding: 30px 40px;
          align-items: center;
        "
      >
        <div style="display: grid; flex-direction: column">
          <span
            style="
              font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif !important;
              font-weight: 700;

              font-size: 14px;
              color: #777;
            "
            >@2021 CHEERS</span
          >
          <span
            style="
              margin-top: 5px;
              font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif !important;
              font-weight: 400;
              font-size: 12px;
              color: #777;
            "
            >경기도 파주시 중앙로 191 스토리빌딩 202호</span
          >
          <span
            style="
              margin-top: 5px;
              font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif !important;
              font-weight: 400;
              font-size: 12px;
              color: #777;
            "
            >대표이사: 공영호 | 사업자등록번호: 412-20-01379</span
          >
          <span
            style="
              color: #ababab;
              font-size: 11px;
              font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif !important;
              font-weight: 400;
              margin-top: 14px;
            "
            >cherrs.fun | E-mail: info@cheers.fun</span
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
